Key Features:
Noise Estimation — Laplacian variance, block-based variance, JPEG artifact detection
Four Algorithms:
Median: Fast, good for salt & pepper (print defects)
Bilateral: Edge-preserving, best for manga (default)
Non-Local Means: Highest quality, heavy noise
Wavelet: Preserves fine details, light noise
Smart Selection — Auto-chooses algorithm based on noise analysis
Manga Presets — mangaScan, webtoon, oldPrint, digital
Web Worker Support — Offload heavy processing for large images
Performance Monitoring — Integrated metrics collection

Usage:

import { createDenoiser } from './denoiser.js';

const denoiser = createDenoiser({ fastMode: false });

// Auto mode
const clean = await denoiser.denoise(imageData);

// Preset
const clean = await denoiser.denoiseWithPreset(imageData, 'oldPrint');

// Manual
const clean = await denoiser.denoise(imageData, {
  algorithm: 'bilateral',
  strength: 0.6,
  sigmaColor: 25
});

